Package kaitech.database

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatabaseHandler
    The DatabaseHandler class controls the setup of database tables, connection to the database, and handles the creation of PreparedStatements for the database to run.
    IngredientTblImpl
    IngredientTblImpl extends AbstractTable, implements the IngredientTable interface, and permits limited access to the data stored in the ingredients table.
